6 0 obj
<< /Length 631 >>
stream
BT /F1 12 Tf 44 720 Td (- Add new sources and more advanced model variants only after the initial MVP shows engagement.) Tj
T* (- Expand to more Svivva mini-app templates and automation recipes as growth tools for users.) Tj
T*
T* (Key success path:) Tj
T* (Make Svivva the platform, not a separate app. Let FeedOS become the intelligence layer that adds value through content understanding, recommendations, and marketing automation.) Tj
T* (Use Pyracrypt to keep the AI stack low-cost, secure, and model-flexible.) Tj
T* (Focus first on product-market fit with one feed, one mood experience, and one mini-app launch story.) Tj
ET
endstream
